 Key activities to mark the 100th anniversary of the founding of the Communist Party of China (CPC), according to a press conference on the anniversary on Tuesday: 1 Party history education 2 President Xi will deliver a speech at a grand ceremony marking CPC's 100th birthday3 Award "July 1 Medal" to distinguished Party members4 Award outstanding Party members, Party affairs workers, community-level Party organizations and senior Party members who have been a member for 50 years5 Visit Party members who have made outstanding contributions, who live in difficulties. Visit the families of martyrs, and the family members of Party officials who died in duty6 Large-scale exhibition 7 Publish CPC-related works, publications 8 Issue commemorative stamps, coins